OL,6,FA Labour councillor has been suspended
OL,7,Fafter he was accused of falling asleep
OL,8,Fduring a briefing aimed at tackling
OL,9,Fchild sexual exploitation.JAlan Atkin
OL,10,Fallegedly nodded off in one of a
OL,11,Fseries of meetings, held on Tuesday,
OL,12,Fto update Rotherham councillors on
OL,13,Fwhat was being done to keep children
OL,14,Fsafe.
