OL,6,FCllr Chris Read, leader of the
OL,7,Fcouncil, said: "The Labour Party takes
OL,8,Ftackling child exploitation incredibly
OL,9,Fseriously and the response of the
OL,10,Fcouncil to threats to children has
OL,11,Fbeen transformed under our leadership
OL,12,Fin recent years, as the presentation
OL,13,Fto Scrutiny showed.J"Cllr Atkin's
OL,14,Fconduct in yesterday's meeting was far
OL,15,Ffrom the standard of professionalism
OL,16,Fand diligence we expect from our
OL,17,Felected officials, and as such we have
OL,18,Fsuspended the whip from Cllr Atkin.
